# Editing Rules
- Only modify selected code
- Do not change unrelated logic
- Do not introduce breaking changes
- Keep existing structure unless necessary

# Refactoring
- Avoid refactoring unless explicitly requested
- Do not rename variables unnecessarily
- Do not reorganize files

# Output
- Make minimal changes
- Keep diff small and focused